1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,200
Master, the fruit has been discarded.

4
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:06,400
Grandpa, was Ji Xuan here just now?

5
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:07,280
Song Zhaoli,

6
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:09,319
you'd throw your life away for Ji Xuan?

7
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,400
Where is Ji Xuan?

8
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:11,680
I need to find her.

9
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,079
Ji Xuan

10
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,519
heard you and Yao
are getting married next month

11
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,680
and has already left.

12
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,519
Who said I'm getting married?

13
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,400
I made that decision for you.

14
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,040
Over my dead body.

15
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,920
Fine.

16
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,879
Alright.

17
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:30,719
I'm curious to find out
whether your bones are harder

18
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,239
or my walking cane is.

19
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:40,439
Grandpa, stop! Are you really
going to beat him to death?

20
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,480
Don't stop me.

21
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:43,280
You don't understand him.

22
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,680
He's a stubborn mule.

23
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,599
He won't bow his head
unless you hit him.

24
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,599
I'm not marrying him.

25
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:50,120
What?

26
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:53,120
Yao, you can't act on impulse.

27
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:54,560
I promise you,

28
00:01:54,739 --> 00:01:56,192
on the first of next month,

29
00:01:56,589 --> 00:01:58,439
the wedding will proceed as scheduled.

30
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,159
Okay?

31
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,159
My decision is made.

32
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,639
My family is prominent and wealthy.

33
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,479
He's unworthy of me.

34
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,520
Yao.

35
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,520
Mr. Song.

36
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,360
Qiu Lin, get the car ready.

37
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,400
I'm going to find Ji Xuan.

38
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,520
Okay.

39
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,520
Mr. Song, the car is ready.

40
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:50,199
Are you sure you're fully recovered?

41
00:02:50,719 --> 00:02:53,159
Grandpa is old.
His strength isn't what it used to be.

42
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,800
Ji Xuan has returned to work, right?

43
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,599
Yes, she has.

44
00:02:58,759 --> 00:03:01,360
Miss Ji expressed her feelings
to the chairman.

45
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,960
But everyone in the group
thinks she's Wu Rui's girlfriend.

46
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,360
How will you

47
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,400
handle public opinion?

48
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,879
(Oh, no. I haven't coordinated
my story with Ji Xuan yet.)

49
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,560
Mr. Song, Mr. Wu is here.

50
00:03:37,344 --> 00:03:38,180
(Termination Notice)
(No.)

51
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,039
(He forced me to go to the restroom.)

52
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:42,000
(I suffered psychological
and physical trauma.)

53
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,520
(And now I'm getting fired?)

54
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,240
(Why is he firing me?)

55
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,919
(Is it because I didn't aim well?)

56
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,120
Mr. Song,

57
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:53,960
did I fail somewhere in my work?

58
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,039
Your work is impeccable.

59
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,639
Then why?

60
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,919
Aren't you dating Ji Xuan?

61
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:02,680
But the person Ji Xuan likes now is me.

62
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,879
Ask Qiu Lin.

63
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,360
He knows everything.

64
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:10,719
He knows Ji Xuan likes me now,

65
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:14,280
and he also knows you two
are fake boyfriend and girlfriend.

66
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,319
So if you stay at Song Group,

67
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,600
it will be very awkward
for Ji Xuan and me.

68
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,720
But rest assured,

69
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:29,000
I will give you an extra severance
in my name.

70
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,639
Sign it.

71
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,240
Mr. Song,

72
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,879
actually, I have a way
that works for everyone.

73
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:40,959
Let's hear it.

74
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:43,839
I will explain to everyone

75
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:46,160
that my feelings for Ji Xuan
are unrequited,

76
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,800
and you and Ji Xuan
are the perfect match.

77
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,920
Are you saying...

78
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,839
I'm saying

79
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,929
I will be your and Ji Xuan's

80
00:04:55,072 --> 00:04:56,160
biggest shipper.

81
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,199
If anyone tries to separate you two,

82
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,079
I will be the first to object.

83
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,120
Mr. Wu,

84
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:04,160
you truly are a flexible
and adaptable talent.

85
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,120
Song Group will not mistreat
any capable employee.

86
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,480
Open it and look.

87
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,600
(Promotion Notice)
From now on,

88
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,560
you are the deputy manager.

89
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,079
Thank you, Mr. Song.

90
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:24,959
Thank you, Mr. Song. Thank you.

91
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,816
You know what?

92
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,240
Before you knew it,

93
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,160
Mr. Song just charged in,

94
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,480
stepped down with his long legs,

95
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,959
knocked the thug
to the ground with one punch,

96
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:41,160
and rescued the woman from danger.

97
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:46,600
Guess who he saved?

98
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,439
Stop teasing. Just tell us.

99
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,399
- Who was it?
- Who was it?

100
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:53,040
It was Miss Ji
who just secured the East City land.

101
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:55,199
Isn't Miss Ji your girlfriend?

102
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,319
Why are you giving credit
to someone else?

103
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,360
Are you giving her away?

104
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,319
Don't talk nonsense here.

105
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,720
Ji Xuan and I...

106
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,439
Ji Xuan is my sister's best friend.

107
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:07,279
So, by that logic,
she's practically my own sister.

108
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:08,720
Being good to her is only right.

109
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,439
Don't badmouth me behind my back.

110
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,079
You hear me?

111
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,279
But isn't Mr. Song with Miss Xie?

112
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:16,600
Miss Xie resigned and left long ago.

113
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,519
Plus, Mr. Song has rejected her
so many times.

114
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,000
Don't pretend you don't know.

115
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,439
Miss Ji and Mr. Song

116
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:25,079
are the perfect match.

117
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,680
Got it?

118
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:29,600
Don't say things
you shouldn't from now on.

119
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,639
I see.

120
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:37,000
Ji Xuan, come with me.

121
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,869
So envious.

122
00:06:43,869 --> 00:06:44,399
Exactly.

123
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,240
Alright, break it up.

124
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,800
Get back to work.

125
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,279
You're all better?

126
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:55,879
Sit.

127
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,240
How much did you raise Wu Rui's salary?

128
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,600
Money? How crude.

129
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,040
I relied entirely on my personal charm.

130
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,720
When did you find out?

131
00:07:10,144 --> 00:07:10,680
About what?

132
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,399
That Wu Rui and I are fake.

133
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,319
From the very start.

134
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,800
Stop pretending.

135
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,680
Do you remember?

136
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,959
When you were with him,

137
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:23,560
your body was quite honest with me.

138
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,120
Just like now.

139
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,240
Qiu Lin told me

140
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:36,160
that you confessed your love to me
in front of Grandpa.

141
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,879
It wasn't that dramatic.

142
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,120
And I remember someone saying,

143
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,680
"If we escape together,
we'll be together."

144
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,560
Ji Xuan,

145
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,519
are we having
that relationship you promised?

146
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,360
Are we?

147
00:07:56,768 --> 00:07:57,399
Yes.

148
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,079
But I have two conditions.

149
00:07:59,279 --> 00:07:59,839
Go on.

150
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:03,399
We date for six months first.
If it works, we continue.

151
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,439
And the other?

152
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,439
Keep work and personal life separate.
We can't go public.

153
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,279
Six months is fine. That's enough time.

154
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,040
I need to head out.

155
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:20,720
After work,

156
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,439
remember to wait for your

157
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:25,160
new boyfriend.

158
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,799
Pour two glasses.

159
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,200
Are you sure?

160
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:58,720
I'm at home with my own boyfriend.

161
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,440
Not afraid to get drunk.

162
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,120
What's up?

163
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:15,000
I suddenly feel like
I'm a concubine being summoned.

164
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,240
♪I think I've lost♪

165
00:09:39,264 --> 00:09:41,840
♪What I thought I had found♪

166
00:09:44,704 --> 00:09:51,120
♪I don't recognize anybody around here♪

167
00:09:52,128 --> 00:09:54,040
♪All the moments we were close♪

168
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:57,760
♪Seem so far away♪

169
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,240
Ji Xuan,

170
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:03,080
I finally have you properly.

171
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,559
Let's eat first.

172
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,000
No.

173
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,519
I want you.

174
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:20,560
♪Only to find out
that it was never enough♪

175
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,440
Whoa! What's up with Song?

176
00:10:46,944 --> 00:10:48,480
(The Other Man)

177
00:10:52,192 --> 00:10:53,408
(Liao)

178
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:57,799
Hello?

179
00:11:14,004 --> 00:11:15,796
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

180
00:11:15,956 --> 00:11:17,836
♪Flickering neon lights♪

181
00:11:18,036 --> 00:11:21,364
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

182
00:11:21,876 --> 00:11:24,148
♪Every star is♪

183
00:11:24,436 --> 00:11:28,308
♪My heartbeat for you♪

184
00:11:29,620 --> 00:11:31,444
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

185
00:11:31,604 --> 00:11:33,156
♪And land in your arms♪

186
00:11:33,556 --> 00:11:37,012
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

187
00:11:37,268 --> 00:11:39,828
♪In the blue sky♪

188
00:11:39,892 --> 00:11:44,020
♪Your smile still lingers♪

189
00:11:44,948 --> 00:11:48,596
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

190
00:11:48,852 --> 00:11:52,516
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

191
00:11:52,724 --> 00:11:55,636
♪Can't find a cure♪

192
00:11:55,636 --> 00:12:00,148
♪To love you after we've parted♪

193
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:04,372
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

194
00:12:04,372 --> 00:12:08,236
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

195
00:12:08,236 --> 00:12:10,036
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

196
00:12:10,132 --> 00:12:15,284
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

197
00:12:15,924 --> 00:12:19,636
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

198
00:12:19,828 --> 00:12:22,580
♪Can't find a cure♪

199
00:12:22,708 --> 00:12:27,348
♪To love you after we've parted♪

200
00:12:27,516 --> 00:12:31,284
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

201
00:12:31,508 --> 00:12:35,092
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

202
00:12:35,316 --> 00:12:37,356
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

203
00:12:37,356 --> 00:12:42,356
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
